OL,3,CHome Office sacks chief immigration
OL,4,Cinspector after airport security row
OL,6,FThe home secretary has sacked the
OL,7,Fimmigration and borders inspector
OL,8,Fafter he claimed thousands were
OL,9,Farriving on private jets without
OL,10,Fpassport checks
OL,12,FBritain's top immigration officer has
OL,13,Fbeen sacked after a claims the UK
OL,14,FBorder Force failed to check hundreds
OL,15,Fof private jets arriving at London
OL,16,FCity airport.
OL,18,FDavid Neal was fired after he
OL,19,F"breached" the terms of his
OL,20,Fappointment, according to the Home
OL,21,FOffice.
