OL,3,CHome Office sacks chief immigration
OL,4,Cinspector after airport security row
OL,6,FShadow home secretary Yvette Cooper
OL,7,Fsaid ministers had been "repeatedly
OL,8,Fwarned about border security risks on
OL,9,Fprivate flights."
OL,11,FShe added: "The prime minister may
OL,12,Fjust think it's all his own mates, but
OL,13,Fthere are real risks from organised
OL,14,Fcrime, money laundering, drugs,
OL,15,Fweapons smuggling, trafficking and
OL,16,Feven terrorism."
