OL,3,CHome Office sacks chief immigration
OL,4,Cinspector after airport security row
OL,6,FA Home Office spokesman said in a
OL,7,Fstatement: "We have terminated the
OL,8,Fappointment of David Neal, the
OL,9,FIndependent Chief Inspector of Borders
OL,10,Fand Immigration, after he breached the
OL,11,Fterms of appointment and lost the
OL,12,Fconfidence of the Home Secretary.
OL,14,F"The planned recruitment process for
OL,15,Fthe next Independent Chief Inspector
OL,16,Fof Borders and Immigration is in
OL,17,Fprogress."
